# Water molecule for simplex minimisation

SystemName          Heavy liquid water, 32 molecules
SystemLabel         32_h2o

LongOutput
WriteCoorXmol
NumberOfAtoms          96
NumberOfSpecies        2

xc.functional          GGA
xc.authors             LYP 

%block ChemicalSpeciesLabel
  1   8  O_lyp
  2   1  H_lyp  
%endblock ChemicalSpeciesLabel

%block AtomicMass
  2   2.0
%endblock AtomicMass

